    "frog, bear and lion).",
    "For sequence-to-sequence translation, GANs form a part of the translation pipeline, replacing ξ -1 m in Fig. 14.",
    "GANs adapt well to new sequences, although they are less robust at a local-scale; this is where transformers excel.",
    "Transformers (Lin et al. 2022; Khan et al. 2022) are predominantly used to model the relationships between different sequences, replacing F in Fig. 14, and place greater attention on local context.",
    "The attention mechanism essentially equates the significance of prior values and their distance from a specific value in a sequence; this process is called self-attention."
